<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8">
    $(document).ready(function() {
        //When page loads...
        $(".tab_content").hide(); //Hide all content
        $("ul.tabs li:first").addClass("active").show(); //Activate first tab
        $(".tab_content:first").show(); //Show first tab content

        //On Click Event
        $("ul.tabs li").click(function() {

            $("ul.tabs li").removeClass("active"); //Remove any "active" class
            $(this).addClass("active"); //Add "active" class to selected tab
            $(".tab_content").hide(); //Hide all tab content
            $(".tab_container").show();
            $(findByLocationButton).show();
            $(findByNameButton).show();
            $(SearchingPleaseWaitDiv).hide();
            searchResultsDiv.hide();
            $(searchFormInputDiv).show();
            $(".goBack").hide();

            $(".tab_content").each(function () {
                $(this).find("p").each(function () {
                    if ($(this).find("input[type='text']").length) {
                        $(this).find("input[type='text']").val($(this).find("label").text());
                    } else if ($(this).find("select").length) {
                        $(this).find("select").find("option:eq(0)").attr('selected', 'selected');
                    }
                });
            });

            var activeTab = $(this).find("a").attr("href"); //Find the href attribute value to identify the active tab + content
            $(activeTab).fadeIn(); //Fade in the active ID content
            return false;
        });
    });
</script>

    var ByNameStateDDL = $('.ByName_state');
    var ByNameStatePTag = $('.ByName_state_p_tag');
    var ByLocationStreet = $('.ByLocation_street');
    var ByLocationCity = $('.ByLocation_city');
    var ByLocationZip = $('.ByLocation_zip');
    var ByNameFirst = $('.ByName_first');
    var ByNameLast = $('.ByName_last');
    var LocatorNotValidated = $('#LocatorNotValidated');
    var SearchingPleaseWaitDiv = $('.SearchingPleaseWaitDiv');
    var HiddenBrandId = $('.HiddenBrandId');
    var HiddenCountriesToUseUrlAppendValueWith = $('.HiddenCountriesToUseUrlAppendValueWith');
    var HiddenUrlAppend = $('.HiddenUrlAppend');
    var HiddenErrorEmailFrom = $('.HiddenErrorEmailFrom');
    var HiddenErrorEmailTo = $('.HiddenErrorEmailTo');
    var HiddenErrorEmailSubject = $('.HiddenErrorEmailSubject');
    var HiddenErrorEmailSmtpHost = $('.HiddenErrorEmailSmtpHost');
    var LocatorErrorMessage = $('.LocatorErrorMessage');
    var HiddenIsLocatorDisabled = $('.HiddenIsLocatorDisabled');
    var HiddenLocatorServiceUrl = $('.HiddenLocatorServiceUrl');

    function ShowResultsIfThere() {
        if (searchResultsDiv.find('li').length > 0) {
            searchResultsDiv.show();
            $(".tab_container").hide();
        } else {
            searchResultsDiv.hide();
        }
    }

    function ByLocationStateDDLHandler(eventObject) {
        var country = $(ByLocationCountryDDL).val();
        $(ByLocationStateDDL).find('option').remove();

        $(HiddenStateDDL).find('option').each(function(index) {
            if ($(this).attr('lang') == country) {
                $(ByLocationStateDDL).append("<option value='" + $(this).text() + "'>" + $(this).text() + "</option>");
            }
        });

        //Check if country is USA or CAN
        if (country == '1' || country == '2') {
            $(ByLocationStatePTag).show();
        } else {
            $(ByLocationStatePTag).hide();
        }

        //Hiding postal code for Ireland
        if (country == '8') {
            $(ByLocationZip).hide();
        } else {
            $(ByLocationZip).show();
        }
    }

    function ByNameStateDDLHandler(eventObject) {
        var country = $(ByNameCountryDDL).val();
        $(ByNameStateDDL).find('option').remove();

        $(HiddenStateDDL).find('option').each(function(index) {
            if ($(this).attr('lang') == country) {
                $(ByNameStateDDL).append("<option value='" + $(this).text() + "'>" + $(this).text() + "</option>");
            }
        });

        //Check if country is USA or CAN
        if (country == '1' || country == '2') {
            $(ByNameStatePTag).show();
        } else {
            $(ByNameStatePTag).hide();
        }
    }

    this.label2value = function() {

        var inactive = "inactive";
        var active = "active";
        var focused = "focused";

        $("label").each(function() {
            //obj = document.getElementById($(this).attr("for"));
            obj = $("input." + $(this).attr("for"));
            if (($(obj).attr("type") == "text")) {
                $(obj).addClass(inactive);
                var text = $(this).text();
                $(this).css("display", "none");
                $(obj).val(text);
                $(obj).focus(function() {
                    $(this).addClass(focused);
                    $(this).removeClass(inactive);
                    $(this).removeClass(active);
                    if ($(this).val() == text) $(this).val("");
                });
                $(obj).blur(function() {
                    $(this).removeClass(focused);
                    if ($(this).val() == "") {
                        $(this).val(text);
                        $(this).addClass(inactive);
                    } else {
                        $(this).addClass(active);
                    };
                });
            };
        });
    };

    $(document).ready(function() {
        $(HiddenStateDDL).hide();
        $(SearchingPleaseWaitDiv).hide();
        $(".goBack").hide();
        ShowResultsIfThere();
        $(goBackToFormLink).click(function() {
            $(findByLocationButton).show();
            $(findByNameButton).show();
            $(SearchingPleaseWaitDiv).hide();
            searchResultsDiv.hide();
            $(searchFormInputDiv).show();
            $(".tab_container").show();
            $(".goBack").hide();

            $(".tab_content").each(function() {
                $(this).find("p").each(function() {
                    if ($(this).find("input[type='text']").length) {
                        $(this).find("input[type='text']").val($(this).find("label").text());
                    } else if ($(this).find("select").length) {
                        $(this).find("select").find("option:eq(0)").attr('selected', 'selected');
                    }
                });
            });
        });

        findByLocationButton.click(function () {
            if (HiddenIsLocatorDisabled.val() === "False") {
                $.ajax({
                    type: "POST",
                    dataType: "json",
                    contentType: 'application/json',
                    cache: false,
                    url: "http://" + HiddenLocatorServiceUrl.val() + "/Portals/8/Services/LocatorResults.asmx/FindConsultantsForLocation",
                    data: JSON.stringify({
                        streetaddress: ByLocationStreet.val(),
                        city: ByLocationCity.val(),
                        state: ByLocationStateDDL.val(),
                        country: ByLocationCountryDDL.val(),
                        zipcode: ByLocationZip.val(),
                        brandId: HiddenBrandId.val(),
                    }),
                    success: function (results) {
                        buildUrls(results);
                    }
                });
            }
        });
        findByNameButton.click(function () {
            if (HiddenIsLocatorDisabled.val() === "False") {
                $.ajax({
                    type: "POST",
                    dataType: "json",
                    contentType: 'application/json',
                    cache: false,
                    url: "http://" + HiddenLocatorServiceUrl.val() + "/Portals/8/Services/LocatorResults.asmx/FindConsultantsByName",
                    data: JSON.stringify({
                        firstname: ByNameFirst.val(),
                        lastname: ByNameLast.val(),
                        state: ByNameStateDDL.val(),
                        country: ByNameCountryDDL.val(),
                        brandId: HiddenBrandId.val(),
                    }),
                    success: function (results) {
                        buildUrls(results);
                    }
                });
            }
        });
        function buildUrls(results) {
            if (results) {
                var listOfCountryIds = new Array();
                var countryId = parseInt(ByLocationCountryDDL.val());
                var urlAppend = HiddenUrlAppend.val();
                var showResults = "<div class='tab_container searchresults'><ul class='locator-results-list'>";
                for (var i in results.d) {
                    if (results.d[i].ExceptionStackTrace != null && results.d[i].ExceptionStackTrace != "undefined" && results.d[i].ExceptionStackTrace != "") {
                        LocatorErrorMessage.text = results.d[i].ExceptionMessage;
                        showResults += "<li>" + results.d[i].Error + "</li>";
                        sendEmail(results.d[i].ExceptionStackTrace);
                        break;
                    }
                    if (results.d[i].PWSUrl === null) {
                        showResults += "<li>" + results.d[i].Error + "</li>";
                        break;
                    }
                    if (HiddenCountriesToUseUrlAppendValueWith.val() != "undefined" || HiddenCountriesToUseUrlAppendValueWith.val() != null || HiddenCountriesToUseUrlAppendValueWith.val() != "") {
                        var listOfCountriesToUseUrlAppendValueWith = HiddenCountriesToUseUrlAppendValueWith.val().split(',');
                        for (var j in listOfCountriesToUseUrlAppendValueWith) {
                            listOfCountryIds.push(parseInt(j));
                        }
                        if (listOfCountryIds.indexOf(countryId) === -1) {
                            urlAppend = "Buy";
                        }
                    } else {
                        urlAppend = "Buy";
                    }
                    var newPwsUrl = results.d[i].PWSUrl.replace("/", "").replace("https:", "").replace("http:", "");
                    showResults += "<li><a href='https://" + newPwsUrl + urlAppend + "' target='_blank'>" + results.d[i].DisplayName + "</a>";
                    showResults += "</li>";
                }
                showResults += "</ul>";
                showResults += "</div>";
                searchResultsDiv.html(showResults);

                $(".tab_container:first").hide();
                SearchingPleaseWaitDiv.hide();
                searchResultsDiv.show();
                $(".goBack").show();
            }
        }
        function sendEmail(body) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                dataType: "json",
                contentType: 'application/json',
                cache: false,
                url: "http://" + HiddenLocatorServiceUrl.val() + "/Portals/8/Services/LocatorResults.asmx/SendMail",
                data: JSON.stringify({
                    erroremailfrom: HiddenErrorEmailFrom.val(),
                    erroremailto: HiddenErrorEmailTo.val(),
                    erroremailsubject: HiddenErrorEmailSubject.val(),
                    erroremailsmtphost: HiddenErrorEmailSmtpHost.val(),
                    body: body
                })
            });
        }

        function SetValidated() {
            $(LocatorNotValidated).hide();

        }

        function SetNotValidated() {
            $(LocatorNotValidated).show();
        }

        function Validate(item) {
            if (!($(item).val())
                || $(item).val() == ''
                || $(item).val() == $(item).prev('label').text()
                || $(item).val() == 'Country'
                || $(item).val() == '*State'
                || $(item).val() == '*Province') {
                SetNotValidated();
                return false;
            } else {
                SetValidated();
                return true;
            }
        }

        $(findByLocationButton).click(submitByLocation);
        $(findByNameButton).click(submitByName);

        function submitByLocation(e) {
            var isValidated = true;
            SetValidated();
            // By Location validation
            if (!Validate(ByLocationStreet)) {
                isValidated = false;
                e.preventDefault();
            }
            if (!Validate(ByLocationCity)) {
                isValidated = false;
                e.preventDefault();
            }
            if (!Validate(ByLocationCountryDDL)) {
                isValidated = false;
                e.preventDefault();
            }

            //Check if location country is USA or CAN
            if ($(ByLocationCountryDDL).val() == '1' || $(ByLocationCountryDDL).val() == '2') {
                if (!Validate(ByLocationStateDDL)) {
                    isValidated = false;
                    e.preventDefault();
                }
            }

            //Check if location country is IRL
            if ($(ByLocationCountryDDL).val() != '8') {
                if (!Validate(ByLocationZip)) {
                    isValidated = false;
                    e.preventDefault();
                }
            }

            if (isValidated == true) {
                $(findByLocationButton).hide();
                $(SearchingPleaseWaitDiv).show();
            }
            return true;
        }

        function submitByName(e) {
            var isValidated = true;
            SetValidated();
            // By Name validation
            if (!Validate(ByNameFirst)) {
                isValidated = false;
                e.preventDefault();
            }
            if (!Validate(ByNameLast)) {
                isValidated = false;
                e.preventDefault();
            }
            if (!Validate(ByNameCountryDDL)) {
                isValidated = false;
                e.preventDefault();
            }

            //Check if name country is USA or CAN
            if ($(ByNameCountryDDL).val() == '1' || $(ByNameCountryDDL).val() == '2') {
                if (!Validate(ByNameStateDDL)) {
                    isValidated = false;
                    e.preventDefault();
                }
            }
            if (isValidated == true) {
                $(findByNameButton).hide();
                $(SearchingPleaseWaitDiv).show();
            }
            return true;
        }

        $(ByLocationCountryDDL).change(ByLocationStateDDLHandler);
        $(ByNameCountryDDL).change(ByNameStateDDLHandler);

        $(ByLocationCountryDDL).val('');
        $(ByNameCountryDDL).val('');

        $(ByLocationCountryDDL).change();
        $(ByNameCountryDDL).change();

        SetValidated();
        label2value();

        //Fix for IE. It was not automatically setting the initial selected country in the list, so it was passing a null value
        if (ByLocationCountryDDL.children(":first")) {
            ByLocationCountryDDL.children(":first").attr('selected', 'selected');
        }

        if (ByNameCountryDDL.children(":first")) {
            ByNameCountryDDL.children(":first").attr('selected', 'selected');
        }

    });
</script>
